Description:
CALL, EMAIL OR TEXT AGENT TO ARRANGE INSPECTION!
SUPERIOR MODERN HOME - GATED REAR ACCESS!
Coming home to 2 Hester Street, Officer will never be something you dont enjoy! As soon as you arrive youll forever be greeted by beautiful established gardens that are perfectly complimented by the one of a kind letterbox!
Situated on an extremely user friendly 584m2 corner block complete with the security of gated side access to the rear for the boat, caravan or trailer. Its not often you can have this level of modern home, this close to amenity and still have vehicle access to the rear!
Inside the home the story just keeps improving! Entering via the front door youll be greeted by a widened entrance and immediately notice the beautiful flow of the home as you step onto the floating timber floors. To the right is a HUGE master bedroom complete with a generous walk in robe and a private ensuite featuring an oversized shower and stylish tiling.
Moving further down the entrance hall, again, to the right is a great sized bedroom 4 that could also be used for a multitude of purposes as it has glass sliding doors to the rear yard. Adjacent to this room is the internal access door to the double remote garage. Continuing on is the first of the living zones with this one being perfectly positioned and really sets the tone of the home as an open formal lounge. Next, is the kitchen! This is the kitchen we all want but so rarely find, featuring beautiful neutral caeserstone counter tops, 900mm freestanding gas cooker, dishwasher and a massive walk in pantry and overlooks the family room, dining room and is absolutely loaded with beautiful natural light! Moving along to the next wing of the home youll find another 2 oversized bedrooms that are serviced by the stylish family bathroom and seperate toilet. This zone is further complimented by a third living room creating the perfect family retreat wing perfect for kids, guests or parents to move in! Some of the extra features also fitted is gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling and solar panels to offset the power bill!
As stated earlier its not often youll find all of this in a property with such a modern vibe and still have the convenience of being perfectly located close to a selection of schools, public transport, shopping options and so much more! Bring your inspection checklist along and youll certainly tick all the boxes here! DONT WAIT! CALL TODAY
Internal area
232.25m²

Description:
Entertainers Paradise & A Finish Like No Other!
Separate Covered Side Access for Caravan/Boat/Trades
Super Size Alfresco with WOW
Stunning Condition
A superior location that delivers the ultimate modern lifestyle, this beautifully presented home has real substance with 3 double bedrooms, exquisite master with dual walk in robe & ensuite with dual vanities and double tiled shower base, bedrooms 2 & 3 with has built in robes, main bathroom is immaculate and virtually new.
Living space is perfectly designed, with a theatre/rumpus room, generous open plan family room with adjoining meals zone, the modern and beautifully appointed kitchen with huge storage, dishwasher, 900mm oven, stone bench tops, glass splash back and pantry.
Enjoy year round entertaining with the Entertainers Alfresco that features a huge space for accommodating outdoor sofas, dining, natural gas point, wiring for speakers and the outdoor woodfire.
The grounds are amazingly presented, the façade of the home is nothing short of jaw dropping with impressive rock pillars either side of the entry, a perfect home with superb energy, the theme of quality, style and beautiful finishes.
First class landscaping with a beautiful water feature/pond, established trees, detail and impressive designer grounds, the side access gates fully lockable will allow you to store a caravan, boat, or tradesman trailers under cover and is quite exceptional.
Highlights-
Immaculate presentation in and out
Split System Cooling
Ducted Gas Heating
Designer Cornice
In Roof Storage
Color Bond Roof
Downlights
Timber Look Flooring
HDMI Points in Living and Outdoor spaces
Exposed Stone Concrete all round
Double remote garage with internal and rear access
Walk to the beautiful park, easy access private & public schools, Beaconsfield town centre, M1 motorway, train station is very easy to access.
A stunning home, great build, and will be very hard to beat!

Description:
Luxurious Castle on a Hill in Grandvue estate!!!
Sitting on an impressive block of land of 531Sqm with a wide side access to the backyard, your new home is located in much sought after Grandvue estate, walking distance to multiple parks, popular schools and shopping centre.
Walk to the front porch and be mesmerised by the view of the valley and distant hills and you will be welcomed by rich engineered timber floors from the front entrance into the heart of the home, a powder room, spacious open plan living/dining area finished with well appointed kitchen with pendent lights, 900mm under-mount stainless steel cooktop & oven, window splash-back, SMEG dishwasher, 40mm stone benchtops, elegant white cabinets, walk in pantry, large stacker door invites you to a covered pergola and designer landscaped backyard with wide side access and large (6m x 3m) shed.
Upstairs comprises of a private living zone, spacious master bedroom to the front of the house with panoramic views, walkin robes, ensuite with double vanity & double shower, three more bedrooms with generous wardrobe spaces serviced by a main bathroom.
Your New Home comes with
- High Ceilings
- Security Alarm
- Ceiling fans to bedrooms
- Elegant pendent lights to Kitchen & Chandelier to staircase
- LED Down lights to downstairs and leisure area in upstairs
- Undermount double bowl sink to kitchen
- Undermount 900mm five burner cook top and oven
- 40mm stone bench top to kitchen
- Stone benchtops throughout the house
- Double lock up garage with internal access to house
- SMEG Dishwasher
- Large shed (6m x 3m)
- Side access to backyard through secured gate (Ideal for your trailer, small boat and/or caravan)
Your new home in 2020 is located walking distance to
- St Francis Xavier College Officer Campus
- St Clare's Primary School
- Parks
- Arena Shopping Centre (Woolworths, post office, chemist shop, gym, reject shop, Mcdonalds)
- Future waterfront & walking tracks
- Pakenham Lakeside Primary School
and short drive to
- Cardinia train station
- Access to monash freeway
- Lakeside village shopping centre (Coles, ALDI, restaurants and cafes)
- The Good guys, Officeworks, Bunnings, JB HIFI
- Pakenham Consolidated School
- Pakenham Secondary College
- Saint Patrick's Primary School
Call Madhawa on 0426 659 974 or Dilshan on 0402 696 602 to schedule a private inspection for you to flow through the house at your own phase with no distractions and feel all this home has to offer.

Your dream home awaits! Timbertop Estate
*518M2 CORNER BLOCK
*POTENTIAL REAR ACCESS FOR BOAT/CARAVAN
*PRIME TIMBERTOP LOCATION
First impressions count for everything and this flawlessly presented Carlisle built home is certainly no exception and will capture you the moment you arrive!
Built to the absolute highest of standards the home makes a real statement with its grand facade, wide open hallway entrance, high ceilings and engineered timber floors. Tailored for those who love to entertain the home has an array of multiple living options, a spacious open plan kitchen offering quality stainless-steel appliances, Caesarstone waterfall bench tops, soft close draws and oversized walk in pantry.
Moving upstairs we have four generously sized bedrooms The executive master suite showcasing pure luxury offering a spacious ensuite complete with over sized shower, double vanity, walk through robe and to top it off your very own private balcony with exceptional views to the north. The 5th bedroom/study is located downstairs and acts as the perfect guest room or home office.
Additional features also include:
Gas ducted heating
Evaporative Cooling & Split System Air Conditioning
Alarm System - Mobile active
CCTV Security Cameras - Mobile Active
Under cover alfresco entertaining area
A prime example of quality and sophistication this stunning home located in the ever popular Timbertop Estate officer is sure to impress and will not disappoint.

Description:
Commanding Home in Superior Location
Located in the exciting Arena Estate, set directly opposite parkland and within close proximity of the shopping centre, access to the M1 Freeway, both private and public schools, child care & early education facilities, public transport and all the amazing amenities this area has to offer.
An elevated position on a large 705m2 block this commanding residence offers over 40 squares of living comprising numerous living zones ideal for the large family.
The home offers:
* Four great sized bedrooms, massive master suite features a large walk in robe and an amazing hotel quality ensuite complete with a spa bath.
* The remaining bedrooms are all a good size and have built in robes
* Four living separate living areas include a formal lounge room that could be used a study
* Modern kitchen offers the master chef stone bench tops, island bench, stainless steel appliances including a 900mm upright oven, dishwasher and loads of cupboard space
* Huge open plan tiled family room with separate dining area
* Home theatre room
* Upstairs rumpus ideal for the kids
* Grand entrance with impressive staircase
* Power room located downstairs ideal for guests
* Massive laundry
* Speaker system throughout the home
* Ducted heating and split system air conditioning
* Double garage with remote control door, rear and internal access
* Undercover entertaining area for year round use
* Lawn area ideal for both kids and pets to play
So much potential for the growing family!
Please note: All property details listed were current at the time of publishing. Due to extreme buyer demand, some properties may have been sold in the preceding 24 hours. Therefore confirmation of all opens with the listing agent within 24 hours of their scheduled opening is advised.

Description:
CLASSY CARLISLE HOME
This home presents an outstanding opportunity to secure a home in the divine Park Central Estate.
Full of modern fixtures and fittings, this is a must add to the inspection list.
Entering the home has a sense of elegance with high ceilings, moving through to the heart of the home is the large kitchen boasting stone bench top, butlers pantry and stainless steel appliances.
The floorplan is well executed with 2 living zones as well as study room which could be converted to a 4th bedroom. The master features WIR and its own ensuite, additional bedrooms all include WIRs and are serviced by the main bathroom.
You will enjoy entertaining in the undercover alfresco that leads out from the main living/dining zone. The hard work has been taken away with the cleverly designed low maintenance garden.
Added features include laundry, double garage, ducted heating and much more.
The Park Central Estate offers a sense of community with its own park, playground and BBQ area and is just minutes from Officers New Proposed Town Centre, local shops and public transport.
This home will not disappoint.

Description:
The Ultimate Entertainers Haven on 823m2
Encapsulating all that is desired in a contemporary family residence, this impressive home situated in the heart of Officer's Arena Estate, boasts an exceptional custom build situated on 823sqm elevated corner block. Complemented by luxurious appointments throughout, whilst offering an interior which exudes style and the exterior leaves nothing to be desired.
The residence features a grand entrance with impressive high ceilings, quality timber flooring flowing into the heart of the home. An extensive family domain incorporating an impressive kitchen with abundance of storage and bench space with 90mm Caesarstone waterfall island bench, stainless steel appliances, built in microwave and Miele dishwasher.
Tailored for entertaining with multiple living areas, with a grand open plan living and dining with built in entertaining unit, formal dining and a second living zone, ensuring all members of the family are catered for.
The master bedroom is surely to impress the most fastidious of buyers, generous in space with an expansive his and hers fitted out walk in robe, every girls dream and serviced by the private ensuite with double vanity, Caesarstone bench, separate toilet and oversized shower. Additional large four bedrooms and fitted with double or triple built in robes and serviced by the main bathroom.
Beautiful bifold doors leading outside to the grand alfresco, this is truly the perfect entertaining home. The outdoor kitchen is a standout, with 90mm Granite benchtops, sink, woodfire pizza oven and built in bar fridges. Enclose the space with bifold glass doors overlooking the immaculate landscaped backyard with the stunning inground swimming pool and slide.
Offering impressive extras, such as ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ducted vacuum, mud room/storage room, laundry with plenty of storage and extra bench space, additional toilet, double remote garage with internal and rear roller door, side access for boats, trailers etc. and so much more.
The Arena Shopping precinct offers a choice of stores including Woolworths, bakery, chemist, medical centre and selection of eateries. Buses also operate throughout the estate and a short walk to Cardinia Train Station and only a stone's throw away from the M1 freeway and primary and high schools within walking distance.
This beautiful home is not one to be missed and is ready for you to make memories of your own!
